data.description:
Seller is offering $10,000 in Concessions! New Roof is being installed and paid off Solar Panels at closing! 
Super Cute and well-maintained home in south Belton in Liberty Valley that’s ready for its new owner! Plenty of room for entertaining as all your living is upstairs! This is a great neighborhood with convenient access to I35, Connell, Hwy 14, and Loop 121. Literally 3 minutes to the Cadence Bank Center, if that. You can be in Georgetown in 30 minutes and 40-ish to Waco. House sits on cul-de-sac lot and no HOA. Garage has epoxy coating on floor.
